 exclusively open to a public vote&nbsp;on&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://www.nykaafashion.com/fashion-vogue-awards.html\">Nykaa.com</a></em>. Ahead of the big night, you get a say in who will be awarded The Emerging Fashion Star of the Year. Will be it be&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/topics/sara-ali-khan/\">Sara Ali Khan</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/topics/janhvi-kapoor/\">Janhvi Kapoor</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/content/ananya-panday-mumbai-home-pali-hill-inside-pictures-bollywood-homes\">Ananya Panday</a>? You decide. You’ll also get a say in who takes home the The Emerging Fashion Star (Male) title—pick between Vicky Kaushal,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/magazine-story/diljit-dosanjh-on-fashion-personal-style-cover-interview-june-2019-vogue-india/\">Diljit Dosanjh</a>, Vijay Deverkonda and more. Do you love&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/topics/arpita-mehta/\">Arpita Mehta</a>’s bold mirror work or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/topics/ridhi-mehra/\">Ridhi Mehra</a>’s pastels? Pick your favourite The Rising Star (Bridal). Similarly, you also get to choose the winners of The Rising Star (Menswear, Womenswear and Accessories). Starting voting now and we will announce your chosen winners at the ceremony.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Stay tuned to this space for more details on Vogue x Nykaa: The Power List 2019, and get live updates from the night on December 9, 2019</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Also read:</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/fashion/content/inside-ekaya-first-ever-flagship-store-in-mumbai-kala-ghoda-palak-shah-textiles\">Ekaya is now in Mumbai: Here\'s everything we know</a></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/fashion/content/presenting-the-winners-vogue-women-of-the-year-2019\">Presenting the winners: Vogue Women Of Th