ooking to upgrade your ethnic wardrobe with a classic drape? Scroll ahead to bookmark your favourites from Janhvi Kapoor’s sari collection.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/instagram {\"url\":\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bwe5t91A5Nv/?utm_source=ig_embed\",\"type\":\"rich\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"instagram\",\"className\":\"\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-instagram wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-instagram\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/Bwe5t91A5Nv/?utm_source=ig_embed\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/instagram -->','Janhvi Kapoor’s sari collection will inspire you to add the six yard staple to your own wardrobe','','inherit','closed','closed','','166-revision-v1','','','2019-11-27 07:26:21','2019-11-27 07:26:21','',166,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/2019/11/27/166-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(171,1,'2019-11-27 07:35:46','2019-11-27 07:35:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It was opposite a vivacious&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/topics/deepika-padukone/\">Deepika Padukone</a>&nbsp;that model&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/content/diana-penty-reveals-her-makeup-skincare-and-perfume-essentials\">Diana Penty</a>&nbsp;made a quiet, assured debut in&nbsp;<em>Cocktail</em>&nbsp;(2012). After her big ticket debut, she returned to the big screen a cool four years later, with&nbsp;<em>Happy Bhaag Jayegi</em>&nbsp;in 2016. Although, Penty has starred in only four other movies since then, the model-turned-actor rose through the ranks as a fashionable name you could bet on. For her first few appearances and promotions before&nbsp;<em>Cocktail</em>&nbsp;hit the screens, Penty highlighted her statuesque lean figure in draped gowns and jumpsuits till 2013. After the release, as the actor got accustomed to the ever-present shutterbugs, her sartorial choices quickly changed to more experimental separates and pantsuits. Here\'s a closer look at her fashion scorecard over the years.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Model Off-Duty</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As the frequency of her outings began, Diana Penty learnt the art of layering instantly with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/content/how-to-style-the-indian-jacket-2-0-like-a-celebrity\">embroidered jackets</a>&nbsp;and blazers often dictated her looks. As her calendar filled up in 2013 with professional commitments, Penty kept pace with her schedule in ruched&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/content/heres-expect-amit-aggarwal-india-couture-week-2018\">Amit Aggarwal</a>&nbsp;gowns and co-ordinated separates that made the best of her 5\'8” frame. In the years that followed, the actor safely left her comfort zone behind in bold colours for the red carpet, taking a emerald-toned beaded gown and a red&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/content/kareena-kapoor-khan-malaika-arora-bollywood-celebrity-guide-to-acing-coordinated-sets\">coordinated pants and blouse set</a>. The only constants that remained throughout,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/content/all-the-celebrity-approved-pantsuits-we-spotted-in-2018\">pantsuits</a>, also saw a change in colour and print. From straight blazers in muted colours to printed co-ords, she tried everything.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>The Cannes debut</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the past two years, Penty has often taken breezy kurtas and flared palazzos for her airport trips, often switching things up with roomy cut-out dresses and her trusty co-ord sets. This year, for her major fashion moment at the Cannes Film Festival, Penty did not shy away from trying on bold colours and textures. She started off with an ethereal stitched sari from Amit Aggarwal, moved onto a romantic floral printed trench coat by Blumarine And finally slipped into a feathery pale pink Nedo by Nedret Taciroglu couture gown and statement jewels by deGrisogno. In the middle, she made sure to turn heads in a lemon yellow bodycon by Atelier Zuhra. Back home, she kept her experimental streak going on with a corset-style lehenga blouse at a wedding reception in Mumbai, and a frayed asymmetric skirt at the Filmfare Awards.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Scroll ahead for our gallery of Diana Penty’s most note-worthy looks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":173,\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2012-3-Diana-Penty.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-173\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\">Diana Penty, 2012</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>© Vogue</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->','Diana Penty’s complete style evolution','','publish','open','open','','diana-pentys-complete-style-evolution','','','2019-11-27 09:21:19','2019-11-27 09:21:19','',0,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/?p=171',0,'post','',0),(172,1,'2019-11-27 07:33:36','2019-11-27 07:33:36','','DIANA-PENTY-FEATURED','','inherit','open','closed','','diana-penty-featured','','','2019-11-27 07:33:36','2019-11-27 07:33:36','',171,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/DIANA-PENTY-FEATURED.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(173,1,'2019-11-27 07:34:26','2019-11-27 07:34:26','','2012-3-Diana-Penty','','inherit','open','closed','','2012-3-diana-penty','','','2019-11-27 07:34:26','2019-11-27 07:34:26','',171,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2012-3-Diana-Penty.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(174,1,'2019-11-27 07:35:46','2019-11-27 07:35:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It was opposite a vivacious&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vogue.in/topics/deepika-padukone