vision','',0),(268,1,'2019-12-02 05:38:22','2019-12-02 05:38:22','<strong>YEAR STARTED : 2017</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>SPECIALITIES : WOMENSWEAR, TROUSSEAU, BRIDAL, ONLINE, READY TO WEAR</strong>\r\n\r\nA mélange of classic crisp cuts and Indian handloom, this elegant luxurious label, is inspired by the old world regalia of Rajasthan in India. Conceptualised and created by the sister-duo Sweta Agrawal and Pallavi Podar, the brand truly reflects the designers and curator\'s innate style and aesthetics. While Sweta can be described by her rich Rajasthani inheritance and her passion to design clothes that appeals to confident strong women, Pallavi caters to the uniqueness and out-of-the-box style of the brand.\r\nAt an opportune time in November 2017, the designers decided to finally convert their passion into a full fledge career and the brand\'s maiden Khadi collection was born.\r\nHand spun and woven, the brand\'s taste in clothing is classic with clean and modern sensibilities in monotones, cutting across the borders and corners of the world. The brand\'s Enchanted Khadi Collection is an expression of true spirit, being a perfect blend of pure natural, soothing fabric with organza and sparkling embellishments. The silhouettes encompass a range of styles from fitted jackets, pants, dresses and co-ords.','A Humming Way','','publish','closed','closed','','a-humming-way','','','2019-12-04 05:32:40','2019-12-04 05:32:40','',0,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/?post_type=portfolios&#038;p=268',0,'portfolios','',0),(269,1,'2019-12-02 05:38:22','2019-12-02 05:38:22','YEAR STARTED : 2017\r\n\r\nSPECIALITIES : WOMENSWEAR, TROUSSEAU, BRIDAL, ONLINE, READY TO WEAR\r\n\r\nA mélange of classic crisp cuts and Indian handloom, this elegant luxurious label, is inspired by the old world regalia of Rajasthan in India. Conceptualised and created by the sister-duo Sweta Agrawal and Pallavi Podar, the brand truly reflects the designers and curator\'s innate style and aesthetics. While Swe