39:48','2019-12-02 05:39:48','',270,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/270-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(272,1,'2019-12-02 05:41:47','2019-12-02 05:41:47','<strong>YEAR STARTED : 2017</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>SPECIALITIES : WOMENSWEAR, TROUSSEAU, BRIDAL, READY TO WEAR, ONLINE</strong>\r\n\r\nBrainchild of designer Usha Devi, Anka is a label that seamlessly blends traditional cream and gold weaves of Kerala with a modern and contemporary feel. The brand experiments with texture and pattern to posit timelessness in a dynamic new market. Their designs embrace and reflect the raw aesthetic of their muse \'modern Kerala\' - which is serene, vibrant and has a sense of simple elegance.\r\nWith a workforce of over hundred and fifty, Anka is an endeavour to revive and sustain the weaving communities of Balaramapuram.','Anka','','publish','closed','closed','','anka','','','2019-12-04 05:33:20','2019-12-04 05:33:20','',0,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/?post_type=portfolios&#038;p=272',0,'portfolios','',0),(273,1,'2019-12-02 05:41:47','2019-12-02 05:41:47','YEAR STARTED : 2017\r\n\r\nSPECIALITIES : WOMENSWEAR, TROUSSEAU, BRIDAL, READY TO WEAR, ONLINE\r\n\r\nBrainchild of designer Usha Devi, Anka is a label that seamlessly blends traditional cream and gold weaves of Kerala with a modern and contemporary feel. The brand experiments with texture and pattern to posit timelessness in a dynamic new market. Their designs embrace and reflect the raw aesthetic of their muse \'modern Kerala\' - which is serene, vibrant and has a sense of simple elegance.\r\nWith a workforce of over hundred and fifty, Anka is an endeavour to revive and sustain the weaving communities of Balaramapuram.','Anka','','inherit','closed','closed','','272-revision-v1','','','2019-12-02 05:41:47','2019-12-02 05:41:47','',272,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/272-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(274,1,'2019-12-02 05:43:10','2019-12-02 05:43:10','<strong>YEAR STARTED : 2017</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>SPECIALITIES : 