 Shah, this unique label casts a spell of glamour and exquisitely alluring designs that create an impression of a lifetime. The brand is known for delivering understated elegance through their tastefully crafted one-of-a-kind ensembles that instantly remind you of a dreamy summer morning. Meticulously bejewelled with rich and vibrant embroideries accentuating indigenous crafts, Shah’s designs bring with them a fresh world charm.\r\n\r\nOffering a range of statement ensembles like shararas, lehengas, anarkalis and other exquisite bridal essentials, the brand is a one stop destination for all things regal. Their Autumn Winter 2019 Collection titled “Ekaa” meaning “One”, is inspired and created by the thought of togetherness. It seamlessly brings together lush colour palettes, festive embellishments and unique silhouettes. Mosaic blue, coral pink, ash crème, flame scarlet, heritage green, ivory blush, yellow iris, galaxy green, opulent black, pretentious purple…the list is endless and they have it all!\r\n\r\nPerfect for brides and bridesmaids alike, the label extends the feeling of power, uniqueness and individuality in each number. Finding the perfect balance between traditional and modern day dressing for weddings, parties and festivities, your search ends here.','Juhi Shah','','publish','closed','closed','','juhi-shah','','','2019-12-04 05:34:43','2019-12-04 05:34:43','',0,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/?post_type=portfolios&#038;p=289',0,'portfolios','',0),(290,1,'2019-12-02 05:55:38','2019-12-02 05:55:38','SPECIALITIES : WOMENSWEAR, PRET, READY TO WEAR, COUTURE, TROUSSEAU, ONLINE\r\n\r\nFounded and spearheaded by designer Juhi Shah, this unique label casts a spell of glamour and exquisitely alluring designs that create an impression of a lifetime. The brand is known for delivering understated elegance through their tastefully crafted one-of-a-kind ensembles that instantly remind you of a dreamy summer morning. Meticulously bejewelled with rich and vibrant embro