WEAR, COUTURE, TROUSSEAU, ONLINE</strong>\r\n\r\nFounded and spearheaded by designer Juhi Shah, this unique label casts a spell of glamour and exquisitely alluring designs that create an impression of a lifetime. The brand is known for delivering understated elegance through their tastefully crafted one-of-a-kind ensembles that instantly remind you of a dreamy summer morning. Meticulously bejewelled with rich and vibrant embroideries accentuating indigenous crafts, Shah’s designs bring with them a fresh world charm.\r\n\r\nOffering a range of statement ensembles like shararas, lehengas, anarkalis and other exquisite bridal essentials, the brand is a one stop destination for all things regal. Their Autumn Winter 2019 Collection titled “Ekaa” meaning “One”, is inspired and created by the thought of togetherness. It seamlessly brings together lush colour palettes, festive embellishments and unique silhouettes. Mosaic blue, coral pink, ash crème, flame scarlet, heritage green, ivory blush, yellow iris, galaxy green, opulent black, pretentious purple…the list is endless and they have it all!\r\n\r\nPerfect for brides and bridesmaids alike, the label extends the feeling of power, uniqueness and individuality in each number. Finding the perfect balance between traditional and modern day dressing for weddings, parties and festivities, your search ends here.','Juhi Shah','','inherit','closed','closed','','289-revision-v1','','','2019-12-04 05:34:43','2019-12-04 05:34:43','',289,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/289-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(314,1,'2019-12-04 05:34:57','2019-12-04 05:34:57','<strong>YEAR STARTED : 2015</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>SPECIALITIES : FLOWERS, GIFT BOXES, ONLINE</strong>\r\n\r\nWorking with fresh and long-lasting flowers, One Roze is a luxury floral atelier, specializing in fresh Ecuadorian preserved roses and unique fresh floral arrangements. The label was founded in 2015 by Keerthi Reddy Kumbam.\r\n\r\nPartners Keerthi Kumbam and Shruthi Malhan were overly fascinated with flowers since a young age. Noticing a huge gap in the market for floral gifting options available in our country Apart from the usual alternatives included the traditional dozen red roses that were being sold everywhere inspired Keerthi to launch the brand ‘ONE ROZE’.\r\n\r\nAn alien concept, the idea of the long-lasting roses (Roses that last for 1-5 years) was something very new. However, with the amazing feedback  that they received they have been able to expand and open at UB city mall, Bangalore.\r\n\r\nOne Roze offers exclusive floral decor services for weddings and other celebratory events. The brand has also recently introduced fresh and preserved bridal bouquets, tiaras and head pieces, which can be customised per the theme.\r\n\r\nThey presently deliver fresh flowers  in Parisian hatboxes, luxury hampers and crates for personal and corporate gifting in Hyderabad and Bangalore and the preserved long-lasting flowers are shipped nationwide.','One Roze','','inherit','closed','closed','','279-revision-v1','','','2019-12-04 05:34:57','2019-12-04 05:34:57','',279,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/279-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(315,1,'2019-12-04 05:35:09','2019-12-04 05:35:09','<strong>YEAR STARTED : 2015</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>SPECIALITIES : FLOWERS, GIFT BOXES, ONLINE</strong>\r\n\r\nWorking with fresh and long-lasting flowers, One Roze is a luxury floral atelier, specializing in fresh Ecuadorian preserved roses and unique fresh floral arrangements. The label was founded in 2015 by Keerthi Reddy Kumbam.\r\n\r\nPartners Keerthi Kumbam and Shruthi Malhan were overly fascinated with flowers since a young age. Noticing a huge gap in the market for floral gifting options available in our country Apart from the usual alternatives included the traditional dozen red roses that were being sold everywhere inspired Keerthi to launch the brand ‘ONE ROZE’.\r\n\r\nAn alien concept, the idea of the long-lasting roses (Roses that last for 1-5 years) was something very new. However, with the amazing feedback  that they received they have been able to expand and open at UB city mall, Bangalore.\r\n\r\nOne Roze offers exclusive floral decor services for weddings and other celebratory events. The brand has also recently introduced fresh and preserved bridal bouquets, tiaras and head pieces, which can be customised per the theme.\r\n\r\nThey presently deliver fresh flowers  in Parisian hatboxes, luxury hampers and crates for personal and corporate gifting in Hyderabad and Bangalore and the preserved long-lasting flowers are shipped nationwide.','One Roze','','inherit','closed','closed','','291-revision-v1','','','2019-12-04 05:35:09','2019-12-04 05:35:09','',291,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/291-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(316,1,'2019-12-04 05:35:22','2019-12-04 05:35:22','<strong>YEAR STARTED : 2011</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>SPECIALITIES : WOMENSWEAR, READY TO WEAR, ONLINE</strong>\r\n\r\nAn Indian collective, SCHÖN is a rapidly growing young label which was launched in 2011 by Sakshee Pradhan. The label specialises in womenswear that encapsulates feminine beauty through its unique style and silhouettes and hails inspiration from the classic era - 1920s to 1950s. Focusing on combining elegance of the colonial era with the edgy modernism of today is what describes SCHÖN in the perfect sense. With a focus on fashion for the modern woman, it marries fashion with practicality in easy silhouettes.\r\n\r\nSCHÖN pronounced as \'she-own’, is a German word that translates to beautiful. The founder and creative head, Sakshee Pradhan is a graduate from The National Institute of Fashion Technology. Having attended workshops and student exchange programs in New York and London, Sakshee has worked with veteran Indian couture designers and is also a proud and active member of the Fashion Design Council of India (FDCI).\r\n\r\nWorking to perfection, the label takes pride in its quality and service and has a loyal clientele not only India, but also in the Middle East (Jeddah, Riyadh & Kuwait), London, Australia (Sydney) & South Africa and tries to bring something refreshing to the table with each of its collections!','Schön by Sakshee Pradhan','','inherit','closed','closed','','281-revision-v1','','','2019-12-04 05:35:22','2019-12-04 05:35:22','',281,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/281-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(317,1,'2019-12-04 05:35:40','2019-12-04 05:35:40','<strong>YEAR STARTED : 2016</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>SPECIALITIES : WOMENSWEAR, TROUSSEAU, PRET, HAUTE COUTURE</strong>\r\n\r\nA fashion design alumna of Instituto Marangoni Milan, Shreeya Somaiya introduced her first collection at the India Runway Week in 2016.\r\nHer design aesthetic focuses on encapsulating the spirit of feminine power with a touch of elegance.\r\nHer creations are beautifully embellished with antique gold sequence with intricate flower details which make the designs distinctly modern and supremely feminine. The collection is both glamorous yet timelessly classic.','Shreeya Somaiya','','inherit','closed','closed','','285-revision-v1','','','2019-12-04 05:35:40','2019-12-04 05:35:40','',285,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/285-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(318,1,'2019-12-04 05:35:53','2019-12-04 05:35:53','<strong>SPECIALITIES : MAKE UP ARTIST, INSTITUTE/ ACADEMY, ONLINE</strong>\r\n\r\nHaving been a back-stage makeup artist at the IIFA awards and the GIMA Awards, while also having worked with leading Bollywood and Tollywood actors, Zorain Khaleeli first perused her passion at the age of 15. The founder of Zorains Studio started her journey in her home town of Bengaluru, focusing only on bridal makeup and photo shoots—and soon moved to Oman. Her expertise in Arabic-style eye finds its roots in the experience she gained there.\r\n\r\nNow conveniently located in the heart of Bengaluru, Zorains Studio is not just a service provider but also a beauty school. The academy sees students from all over India and overseas. With a large number of in-house and visiting faculty, it offers multiple courses that cover hair, makeup, nails, lashes and more, for a technically detailed development of the trainee.\r\n\r\nKhaleeli has also worked with MAC Cosmetics for a decade and according to her, working at the counter has given her the kind of experience she couldn\'t have gained anywhere else. \"Working with real life people is the biggest asset to learning the art of makeup. Each individual is unique and beautiful in their own way and to work with each one\'s face anatomy is a science in itself,\" she says.\r\n\r\nShe has also been a part of 12+ seasons of India Fashion Week as well as others like Blenders Pride Fashion Week and Couture Week. Bringing all her experience and expertise together, she has successfully carved a niche for her brand that marries service, product and training in a seamless manner.','Zorains Studio','','inherit','closed','closed','','293-revision-v1','','','2019-12-04 05:35:53','2019-12-04 05:35:53','',293,'http://dev.evantiv.com/vogue_wp/293-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(320,1,'2019-12-04 05:49:46','2019-12-04 05:49:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SPECIALITIES :&nbsp;</strong><strong>MAKE UP ARTIST, INSTITUTE/ ACADEMY, ONLINE</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Having been a back-stage makeup artist at the IIFA awards and the GIMA Awards, while also having worked with leading Bollywood and Tollywood actors, Zorain Khaleeli first perused her passion at the age of 15. The founder of Zorains Studio started her journey in her home town of Bengaluru, focusing only on bridal makeup and photo shoots—and soon moved to Oman. Her expertise in Arabic-style eye finds its roots in the experience she gained there.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now conveniently located in the heart of Bengaluru, Zorains Studio is not just a service provider but also a beauty school. The academy sees stude